gdn.sh — PoHW Verification Node [00]

STATUS: Active
PROTOCOL: Proof of Human Work v1.0.0
SIGNATURE FORMAT: SHA-256 • Ed25519

This node provides stateless verification endpoints for Proof of Human Work attestations.

VERIFICATION ENDPOINTS:
- GET /pohw/verify/index.json — Node status and metadata
- GET /pohw/verify/index.cjson — Canonical JSON for hashing
- GET /pohw/verify/index.sig.bin — Binary signature file

VERIFICATION:
Upload file + signature → GET verdict (valid/invalid + signer DID + timestamp)

PUBLIC KEY:
https://gdn.sh/.well-known/public.txt

PROTOCOL SPECIFICATION:
https://proofofhumanwork.org/spec

